      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/germany/living/climate-seasons-turkey-vs-germany/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Climate &amp;amp; Seasons: Turkey vs Germany&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;climate--seasons-turkey-vs-germany&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#climate--seasons-turkey-vs-germany&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I knew German winters would be grey. I didn&amp;rsquo;t know how grey. Or how beautiful the summers would be.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;🇹🇷 Turkey: Sun as Default&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;-turkey-sun-as-default&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#-turkey-sun-as-default&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Turkey&amp;rsquo;s climate varies dramatically by region — the Aegean and Mediterranean coasts offer warm, dry summers and mild winters; the Black Sea region is lush and rainy; central Anatolia gets genuine cold snaps in winter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
